  associates the map 1_\Omega  to some subobject \omega \xhookrightarrow {\top }\Omega .
  Now suppose we are given a subobject s\hookrightarrow  x, associated by the
  representation to a map x\xrightarrow {\chi _s}\Omega . Naturality of the
  representation asserts that the diagram 




